      • close

        public void close(String sName)
        Description copied from interface: es.unex.sextante.core.IInputFactory
        Closes (eliminates it from the application running SEXTANTE) a data object (table or layer) given its name. If it is not opened in the application (for example, not being shown in a view or map), but it is contained in the input factory list of objects (such as layers loaded using the open() method from the command-line interface), it should remove it from that list.
        Parameters:
        sName - the name of the data object to close
